OL,3,CChancellor declines to rule out income
OL,4,Ctax hike ` reports
OL,6,FRachel Reeves has declined to rule out
OL,7,Fraising income tax at next month's
OL,8,FBudget, according to reports.
OL,10,FThe Chancellor has previously insisted
OL,11,Fthat Labour's manifesto commitment not
OL,12,Fto raise income tax, national
OL,13,Finsurance or VAT "stands" when
OL,14,Fquestioned about how she will bridge a
OL,15,Ffiscal black hole in November.
