OL,3,CChancellor declines to rule out income
OL,4,Ctax hike ` reports
OL,6,FBut asked about reports the Treasury
OL,7,Fwas considering an income tax hike,
OL,8,Fthe BBC said Ms Reeves told reporters
OL,9,Fon Friday she would "continue to
OL,10,Fsupport working people by keeping
OL,11,Ftheir taxes as low as possible" but
OL,12,Fwas still "going through the process"
OL,13,Fof writing the Budget.
OL,15,FThe Chancellor said: "Although I can't
OL,16,Ftalk about individual measures at this
OL,17,Fstage, I understand that the cost of
OL,18,Fliving is still people's number one
OL,19,Fconcern."
