OL,3,CChancellor declines to rule out income
OL,4,Ctax hike ` reports
OL,6,FMs Reeves is widely expected to use
OL,7,Fthe Budget to increase taxes once
OL,8,Fagain, with the Institute for Fiscal
OL,9,FStudies estimating she needs to find
OL,10,F#22 billion of tax rises or spending
OL,11,Fcuts to meet her self-imposed fiscal
OL,12,Frule.
OL,14,FThe gap comes as a result of higher
OL,15,Fborrowing costs, weak growth and an
OL,16,Fexpected downgrade to official
OL,17,Fproductivity forecasts, although
OL,18,Frecent better-than-expected inflation
OL,19,Ffigures have eased the pressure
OL,20,Fslightly.
