OL,3,CChancellor declines to rule out income
OL,4,Ctax hike ` reports
OL,6,FRaising the basic rate of income tax
OL,7,Fby 1p could raise around #8 billion,
OL,8,Fbut would break a clear manifesto
OL,9,Fpledge.
OL,11,FIt would also be the first time the
OL,12,Fbasic rate has been increased since
OL,13,Fthe 1970s.
OL,15,FThe Chancellor is also reported to be
OL,16,Fconsidering cutting the amount of
OL,17,Fmoney people can save in cash Isas as
OL,18,Fpart of a drive to encourage
OL,19,Finvestment in stocks and shares.
