OL,3,CChancellor declines to rule out income
OL,4,Ctax hike ` reports
OL,6,FIt is understood that no decision has
OL,7,Fyet been made and several options are
OL,8,Fbeing considered, including halving
OL,9,Fthe allowance from #20,000 to #10,000.
OL,11,FTreasury minister Lucy Rigby told the
OL,12,FTelegraph the Government was "looking
OL,13,Fat the right balance between cash and
OL,14,Fshares in the Isa".
OL,16,FShe said: "The bottom line is, we want
OL,17,Fpeople to be better off and one way we
OL,18,Fcan do that is to build a shareholding
OL,19,Fdemocracy in this country."
